{"tid":343620,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"屌 個蔡若蓮做教育局副局長真係無得救","createTime":"2017-08-01T15:07:46.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-07T14:26:00.000Z","uid":17554,"like":20,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e58f15f9b956571a1a67752bb5dc61a9eff977fa","tid":343620,"uid":17554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T15:07:46.000Z","msg":"身為老師（非語文科）見到咁嘅垃圾做副局長真係火都嚟撚埋 明明教育界已經聯署曬 立法會佢選教育界功能組別佢大敗 以前佢做中文科課程主任搞普教中仲到一pat屎咁既人都可以做教育局副局長 香港真係無得救<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n佢以前不斷推普廢粵 不斷推「普教中」最後衰咗先迫住走 佢走嘅時候仲賴點解香港學校唔全面用普通話授課 我聽到真係屌曬老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n各位巴絲打 勸大家將來生仔女唔好比佢地係香港主流學校讀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 老師我可以唔做 但唔好比我地下一代較飛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"160485ea5f3526e96500c0c03bd77ddaa875ffaa","tid":343620,"uid":2959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T15:08:55.000Z","msg":"玩完啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d94a2b5bda66e4d37021de51b276a2e713ba1f9b","tid":343620,"uid":838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T15:09:07.000Z","msg":"「用人唯才」喎"},{"pid":"f5f910e9d4f9a8b6bbc4c74300cd49d2bfa13bcd","tid":343620,"uid":17554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T15:15:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>玩完啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n真心 「金翅挽撚猿」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e4949706f1794d1d4f2414a1f23b3c7f3142841","tid":343620,"uid"