br />\n仲有個教評，應該都已經被招安左</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n教評 同 教聯 都係啲左派<br />\n<br />\n得教協正常啲"},{"pid":"a43deb14e0b99fbc7b82b263daaad475632dd929","tid":343620,"uid":17554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T15:58:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>罷課<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n大專生罷課都話易<br />\n<br />\n中學生無可能 考公開試教慢啲都畀人屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0894a1adda4bfee77758e209274cc980526896ee","tid":343620,"uid":54959,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T16:02:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>落選可升官發財是常識吧 ?</blockquote><br />\n做唔到議員，就改為做官，騎係上面隊撚住你班民主派"},{"pid":"c4aae72bcc2c02f7d7ef23f60a73ece8eab08f1c","tid":343620,"uid":30476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T07:43:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0f26a65f125688b84dbde81fe8f87ae379c4fbe","tid":343620,"uid":48124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T14:26:00.000Z","msg":"binc<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}